>If you want a three point belts in the back seat of a 1970 Riviera you're 
>probably going to have to mount *something* to a cabinet, or modify the 
>cabinetry somehow. I am no expert on early bay's buses or Rivieras but 
>IIRC the factory didn't start putting mounting brackets in for a shoulder 
